               stealing a muslin gown, value 10 s. two blankets, value 6 s. three dimity waistcoats, value 10 s. four stuff bed curtains, value 10 s. three stuff window curtains, value 3 s. a copper stew-pan, value 1 s. 6 d. a damask tablecloth, value 1 s. a dimity petticoat, value 6 d. a linen shirt, value 4 s. and a flannel petticoat, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17810425-13-victim175" type="victimName">
